      <title>市场复苏带动业绩回升，平安利润上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/ping-an-profit-rises-as-market-recovery-bolsters-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[平安保险（集团）股份有限公司宣布，上半年利润增长近 7%，受股市复苏提振，这家中国市值第二大保险公司的投资回报有所提升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/ping-an-profit-rises-as-market-recovery-bolsters-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 10:03:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球需求担忧加剧，油价维持在 1 月低点附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国经济放缓和 2025 年前景疲软的担忧抵消了库存下降带来的提振，油价稳定在 1 月份以来的最低收盘价附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 23:27:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
